---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" title="Legal Notice — Fab Verbatim" description="Legal notice of Fab Verbatim. Information about the website owner, intellectual property and terms of use.">
  <Nav lang="en" currentPage=""/>
  <main>
    <div class="page-hero"><div class="page-hero-inner reveal"><p class="eyebrow eyebrow--light">Legal</p><h1>Legal Notice</h1><p>Law on Information Society Services (LSSI)</p></div></div>
    <section class="legal-body">
      <div class="legal-inner reveal">
        <p class="legal-intro">Fabienne Colette Marie Françoise Annys, website owner, makes this document available to users in order to comply with the obligations laid down in Law 34/2002 of 11 July on Information Society Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSICE), and to inform all website users of the conditions of use.</p>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">1. Identification data</h2><div class="legal-data-grid"><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Legal name</span><span class="legal-data-val">Fabienne Colette Marie Françoise Annys</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Trading name</span><span class="legal-data-val">Fab Verbatim</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">NIF</span><span class="legal-data-val">X1233450Y</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Address</span><span class="legal-data-val">Carrer Sant Pere nº 7, Sant Climent de Llobregat, 08849 Barcelona, Spain</span></div><div class="legal-data-row"><span class="legal-data-label">Email</span><span class="legal-data-val"><a href="mailto:contact@fabverbatim.com">contact@fabverbatim.com</a></span></div></div></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">2. Purpose</h2><p class="legal-p">Through this Website, we offer users the possibility of accessing information about our translation services.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">3. Privacy and data processing</h2><p class="legal-p">When access to certain content or services requires personal data, users guarantee the accuracy and authenticity of such data. The company will process said data in accordance with its nature and purpose, as detailed in the <a href="/en/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">4. Industrial and intellectual property</h2><p class="legal-p">The user acknowledges that all website content — including designs, texts, images, logos, icons, software, trade names and trademarks — is subject to intellectual and industrial property rights owned exclusively by the company or third parties. The user undertakes not to reproduce, copy, distribute or modify such content without express authorisation.</p></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">5. User obligations</h2><ul class="legal-list"><li>Make lawful and appropriate use of the website and its content.</li><li>Not carry out unlawful or illegal activities.</li><li>Not attempt to access restricted areas without meeting the required conditions.</li><li>Not introduce computer viruses or any other harmful systems.</li></ul></div>
        <div class="legal-section"><h2 class="legal-h2">6. Applicable law and jurisdiction</h2><p class="legal-p">These conditions are governed by Spanish law. Any dispute shall be submitted to the Courts and Tribunals of the registered office of the website owner.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en"/>
</Layout>
<style>
  .legal-body{background:var(--white);padding:5rem 4rem}.legal-inner{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto}.legal-intro{font-size:0.97rem;font-weight:300;color:#2a2a2a;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:1.2rem}.legal-section{margin-top:2.5rem;padding-top:2.5rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}.legal-h2{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em}.legal-p{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:300;color:#2a2a2a;line-height:1.9;margin-bottom:0.9rem}.legal-p a{color:var(--gold);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px}.legal-list{margin:0.8rem 0 0.8rem 1.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.6rem}.legal-list li{font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:300;color:#2a2a2a;line-height:1.8}.legal-data-grid{display:flex;flex-direction:column;border:1px solid var(--border);margin-top:1rem}.legal-data-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:160px 1fr;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}.legal-data-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}.legal-data-label{font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--navy);padding:0.85rem 1rem;background:var(--blue-tint);border-right:1px solid var(--border)}.legal-data-val{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:300;color:#2a2a2a;padding:0.85rem 1rem}.legal-data-val a{color:var(--gold)}
  @media(max-width:900px){.legal-body{padding:4rem 1.5rem}.legal-data-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}.legal-data-label{border-right:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}}
</style>
<script>const obs=new IntersectionObserver((e)=>{e.forEach((en,i)=>{if(en.isIntersecting)setTimeout(()=>en.target.classList.add('visible'),i*60)});},{threshold:0.07});document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(el=>obs.observe(el));</script>
